    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been such a joy to drive! It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily errands and road trips. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for a new owner to take the wheel. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, providing a tactile connection to the rear-mounted limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, with recent attention paid to the rear subframe mounting points and trailing arm bushings to ensure precise lateral stability and sharp turn-in. While the aesthetics reflect its status as a dedicated driver\u2019s car with minor honest wear, the powertrain remains robust, delivering a visceral induction note and a linear torque curve up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Ideal for the enthusiast seeking a pure, naturally aspirated experience with sorted mechanicals.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
