    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and is ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
