    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, paired with a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example features a reinforced rear subframe and a recently serviced VANOS system, addressing the chassis and valvetrain concerns common to the platform. The M-Variable Differential Lock provides exceptional traction out of corners, while the factory-tuned suspension retains its composure under high lateral loads. Though the finish shows minor pebble peppering on the front fascia, the core performance attributes\u2014including the individual throttle bodies and linear power delivery\u2014remain uncompromised. An honest, driver-centric machine for the discerning purist.",
